text:
An OG meet up place in the CBD with good drink bundles and great indochinese food. The staff here are especially nice and always ready to chat. Great place!

I highly recommend the fried rice, lao pho, and truffle fries
Doreen is a nice service crew. She is friendly , chatty and provide good service . She clears our table before serving the dessert
No complaints abt this plc n that's why i'm every @ least twice.... The chef is amazing, she cook to impress n people who works there... Excellent

I was invited to join a crowd there for dinner, and I didn't make the order. However, their platter and fried rice are delicious. It is a treat from the host thus no price awareness. Judging from the location and quality, I would say it is not cheap.
Friendly joint with good choice of wines reasonably priced. Food was good with Vietnamese / Laos mix. Will be back when we canâ€¦
